The RFID::Base package provides abstract base classes and helper
functions for implementing RFID reader and tag classes.

See the perldoc for RFID::Reader and RFID::Tag for documentation.

See the rfid-perl Web page for other information, and instructions for
subscribing to the mailing list:

    http://whereabouts.eecs.umich.edu/code/rfid-perl/ 

